wAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2999.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Rogues - gotta love em :P</span><hr size=1> Right ledge group in LOIO. Shammy, cleric, and chanter (me) recruit a rogue to fill one of the tank slots.<br>
<br>
While waiting for some real tanks to show up we pulled a few singles to keep busy.<br>
<br>
Shammy asks rogue if hes pickpocketing...shes noticed on the few mobs shes looted that coin is very low...and having a rogue primary she knows where its gone <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Rogue replies that he pickpockets all the time. Shammy tells him thats fine but he better be prepared to split what he takes off the mobs.<br>
<br>
Rogue says what'll he do instead is not loot any of the mobs but only keep what he pickpockets.<br>
<br>
I point out that the crap thats left isn't really worth looting anyway.<br>
<br>
