<br>
Me <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ukerryndarkwater.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kerryn Darkwater</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 988<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/8/02 4:31:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2999.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogues - gotta love em :P</span><hr size=1> Would want to see what was actually said first.<br>
<br>
I tell you where the post begins to feel bad for me<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> ...shes noticed on the few mobs shes looted that coin is very low...and having a rogue primary she knows where its gone<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
