</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ufeathersilverthorn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Feather Silverthorn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 170<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/8/02 9:47:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2999.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogues - gotta love em :P</span><hr size=1> Back when I was playing Feather all the time. I picked all the time.<br>
<br>
Of course I split it at the end. And most of the time I was the master looter anyways.<br>
